<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.4.1">
<l>ēṉamu ṉāki yirunila miṭantaṉ</l>
<l>ṟiṇaiyaṭi yimaiyavar vaṇaṅka</l>
<l>tāṉava ṉākan taraṇiyil puraḷat</l>
<l>taṭañcilai kuṉittaven talaivaṉ</l>
<l>tēṉamar cōlaik kaṟpakam payanta</l>
<l>teyvanaṉ ṉaṟumalar koṇarntu</l>
<l>vāṉavar vaṇaṅkuṅ kaṅkaiyiṉ karaimēl</l>
<l>vatariyāc ciramat tuḷḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our leader who bent the long bow</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the body of the Dānava rolled to earth</l>
<l>As the unblinking [celestials] then adored both of [his] feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">having long ago become a boar digging up the vast earth,</l>
<l>He is the one in Badarī Āśrama on the banks of the Ganges</l>
<l rend="indent">where heavenly beings worship,</l>
<l>Bringing fine, fragrant, divine flowers which the kalpaka tree yields</l>
<l rend="indent">in the honey-filled grove.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
